{
  "arquivo": "ca03_30",
  "total": 154,
  "dialogos": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "Thank you all very much for waiting!\\nWe will now begin today's couple contest!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "Alright, all participants,\\nplease come up to the stage!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "It looks a lot more serious than we imagined?\\nI thought it was going to be a smaller event.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Y-yeah,\\nthere are quite a lot of people participating.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "And quite a large audience as well...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "personagem": "Hasty Guy",
      "texto_en": "Ah! Isn't that her?\\nThe one from team A!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "personagem": "Excited Guy",
      "texto_en": "WAAA!\\nThat girl is SUPER cute!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "personagem": "Spectator Girl",
      "texto_en": "Hmmm?\\nI feel like I've seen that girl somewhere before.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "personagem": "Forgetful Girl",
      "texto_en": "Me too.\\nDoes she look like someone else?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Ooohh...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Hey, wouldn't it cause a commotion\\nif it's revealed that Ichika\\nis in the audience, in a situation like this?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Well, she disguised herself earlier with glasses,\\nso I think it's fine...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Well, Ichika should know how to behave\\n in this kind of situation, so it should be okay.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "But anyway, what should we do?\\nWe could just slack off and lose right away%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "personagem": "Yotsuba",
      "texto_en": "U-e-su-gi-saaan!\\nMikuuu! Do your best!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "So, well, since we're being cheered on like that,\\nI guess we can't just lose on purpose now.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "...Okay.\\nAnd, I...told everyone, too.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "That Futaro's mine.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "!...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "So, losing in front of everyone\\nwould be a bit too much.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Okay.\\nSo, let's win.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "Alright, then, now I'll explain the rules.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "Each team will attempt three games,\\nand if they successfully complete two of them,\\nthey will pass the challenge.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "The couples who have passed the challenge\\nand demonstrated the most lovey-dovey attitude\\nwill be voted on by the audience.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "The couple who receives the most votes\\nwill be recognized as today's best couple!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "The first game is 'Eye Contact for Eternity'!\\nWe'll commence the contest immediately!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "Now! As you can see, a special juice is placed\\nbetween the two lovebirds,\\nlying facing each other on the sandy beach!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Futaro...\\nThis cup has two straws in it...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "No way...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "The couples will have to drink all of this juice\\nwhile looking at each other!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I knew it...!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "If you don't drink all the juice in time, you're out.\\nAnd if you lose eye contact with your partner,\\nyou'll be disqualified.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "Are you ready?\\nNow, let's START!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Oooohh?!\\n When I put the straw in my mouth,\\n Miku's face is so close to mine!!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Such close range is indeed...)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "~~~~~!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "Oh? What's wrong with Team A?\\nIf you don't drink it quickly,\\nyou'll be disqualified!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Nnnnn!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "Oh! What vigor!\\nCome on, Mr. Boyfriend, you can't be losing now!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(I get that, you don't need to say anything!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "NNNNNN!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Nn-nnnn...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "NNNNNN?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Miku?!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Nn-nnnn...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(I-I understand how she feels!\\n It's quite embarrassing to stare at each other\\n at such close range! I wanna look away!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 46,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Then, I've gotta drink it all before Miku looks away!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 47,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Miku, look ONLY at me!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 48,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Huh, Futaro?\\nYou're gonna drink all of it?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 49,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Oo-ooohh...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 50,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(My stomach is bloated...\\n That was really close...)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 51,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Futaro, are you alright?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 52,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "O-of course! This is nothing!\\nHahahahahaha!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 53,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Great job, Miku!\\nThanks to you not looking away,\\nI was able to finish until the end%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 54,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Oooh!\\nSorry, let me take a break.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 55,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "...You told me...to ONLY look at you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 56,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "The next game is 'Princess in Arms'!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 57,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "The men will have to princess carry their partner and hold that\\nposition until time's up! If your partner's body\\ntouches the ground, it's game over.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 58,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 59,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Futaro, don't try too hard.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 60,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "N-no!\\nI can definitely do this!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 61,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "And, START!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 62,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "HHNGH!!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 63,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "W-WAWA?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 64,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(A-alright!\\n I can do this!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 65,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Amazing, Futaro.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 66,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Ha-hahaha!\\nTh-this, a-ain't, n-nothing!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 67,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "But, don't strain yourself...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 68,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I-I'm not straining myself!\\nJust, a little, more%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 69,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I can't hold it!\\nI'm sorry, I gotta put you down!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 70,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "W-WOAH?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 71,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "Oh, wow!\\nThe boyfriend got his foot caught in the sand and fell down,\\nbut managed to get underneath her in time and protected her from the impact!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 72,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Owww...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 73,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Are you okay, Futaro?!\\nAre you injured?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 74,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I-I'm fine.\\nThe impact wasn't as bad as I thought.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 75,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "...Does that mean,\\nyou thought I was heavier than I actually am?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 76,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Huh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 77,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "You did think that, huh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 78,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "No, that's not what I meant!\\nI just meant that I was able to take the fall properly%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 79,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 80,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "Wow, take a look at this!\\nEven after falling, they're still so lovey-dovey!\\nYou guys are such a great couple!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 81,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "HUH?!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 82,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "Unfortunately, you didn't pass this round,\\nbut the venue is full of smiles!\\nThank you for sharing your happiness with us!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 83,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Auuuhh...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 84,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(It's one win and one loss so far.\\n The next game is the deciding round.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 85,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "Finally, it's the last game!\\nThe third game is 'I Love You, Over and Over Again'!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 86,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(...This is the most unpleasant title so far.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 87,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "Both of you will take turns saying 'I love you.'\\nIf you blush or laugh, you lose!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 88,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(Just as I suspected!\\n A public love confession?!)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 89,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I-impossible!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 90,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "Let's get started,\\nhere we gooo!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 91,
      "personagem": "High-Spirited Guy",
      "texto_en": "I LOVE you!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 92,
      "personagem": "Cheerful Girl",
      "texto_en": "Me too! I love you so much!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 93,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(No way...\\n Everyone around us is chanting\\n 'I love you' in chorus...)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 94,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I-... I-...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 95,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I-... I, lo%p-2;――%p;!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 96,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I-... I lo%p-2;――%p;!\\nOoohh...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 97,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "......",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 98,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Hey, Futaro.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 99,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Wh-what is it?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 100,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "This is like, that time, kinda.\\nAt the school festival...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 101,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "(...When I confessed.)",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 102,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I wanted to convey my feelings to you back then,\\nbut I couldn't put it into words,\\nand ended up crying...causing trouble to you.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 103,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "I wasn't troubled by that.\\nI told you before,\\nI've never been troubled by you, Miku.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 104,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Yeah...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 105,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 106,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I like you, now more than I did back then, Futaro.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 107,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "!...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 108,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "M-me, too.\\nI like you...now more than I did back then, too, Miku.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 109,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "I like you more.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 110,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "No, I do.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 111,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "No, it's me%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 112,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Teehee!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 113,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "...Hahaha!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 114,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "Team A, I'm so sorry!\\nYou've laughed, so you're out!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 115,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "Thank you for waiting!\\nThe audience votes have been tallied,\\nand now it's time for the results!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 116,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "We won't be chosen, will we?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 117,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Yeah, we only cleared one game.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 118,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "The winner is%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 119,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "The couple from Teeeam A!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 120,
      "personagem": "Futaro",
      "texto_en": "Huh?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 121,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "Wh-why...?",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 122,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "Alright, you two!\\nCome on up to the front!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 123,
      "personagem": "Miku",
      "texto_en": "H-huh...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 124,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "Well-as you can see,\\neven the winners themselves are surprised\\nby this turn of events...",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 125,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "Actually, the two of you were not originally\\nincluded in the voting,\\nbut you clearly deserved the first place!",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 126,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "After conducting a brief evaluation%p-2;――",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 127,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "When the boyfriend fell, he made himself the cushion,\\nwhich was cool.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 128,
      "personagem": "Officiant",
      "texto_en": "Their performance in the last round\\nwas so youthful and dazzling, to the point\\nthe people have decided that there is no one else worthy of first place but them.",
      "texto_ptbr": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 129,
